  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To provide multi purpose cash transfer, hygiene kits and awareness to marginalised to fight Covid</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">300 HH to receive cash in hand to help them to spend according to their needs.  Also hygiene kits to 300 HH will to support in prevention of covid.  Awareness on Covid and vaccine to most marginalised community to help in containment of disease</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project intervention would be in Simdega and Kunti districts and Bano &amp;Torpo blocks of Jharkhand where the population are extremely marginalized and belongs to tribals community.  The project to provide a) multi purpose cash transfer of Rs. 3000/- to 300 HH b) 300 HH to receive hygiene kits c) 6000 people to receive awareness on covid appropriate  behaviour and vaccination drive.  volunteers and project staff to provide with safety kits to collect information and documents to initiate bank transfer to beneficiaries.</narrative>
  </description>
